      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEREFORAGOODTIME (2) drew wide last start and was never a genuine threat, beaten 8 metres into fifth at this track over 1800m. Must raise the bar but from a far better starting position a big run is on the cards. CLARENDEN LEGACY (3) last raced four weeks ago when he scored a game win over 1800m here, getting home by 1.75 metres after finding the lead in the early stages. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw and his last-start form is good enough to win a race of this calibre. MAGIC CAPTAIN (7) is in the mix at his first run since scoring over 1800m at this circuit eight months ago. Can run a race while fresh. CAPTAIN BARNATO (9) is in the mix following a respectable third at his most recent appearance over 2230m at this venue. One for the multiples.",
